        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Now if P(x) = ∑j=0ajxj, then the relation P(x) = Cx2 (x) implies that aj = Cj(j − 1)aj for al ; hence aj = 0 for j ≤ n− 1, and we conclude that P(x) = axn, which has all identical roots.",
